@model RpgHBAnnals.Model.Weapon.WeaponCreate

@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Create";
}
<div class="Head">
    <h2>Create</h2>
    <br/>
    <p>
        Nice to see you here! Just a bit of advice, <b>Keep It Simple</b> that way you dont have to agonize over every detail and everyone who come across your creation can adapt it while keeping the core attrubutes alive. You can still write a novel in the properties section if you want though. Can't wait to see what you make!
